## How to Run

1. Clone the repository:
```bash
   git clone https://github.com/PalakKumar22/Economic-Data-Analysis.git
```
2. Install dependencies:
```bash
   pip install pandas matplotlib jupyter
```
3. Launch Jupyter:
```bash
   jupyter notebook
```
4. Open any `.ipynb` file and run all cells.

